docs.text: How to connect? Use either of the following addresses to connect to CraftedLands play.craftedlands.net mc.craftedlands.org skyblock.co.nz (Will join straight to Skyblock server) Current Server Version: 1.8+ Stuck? Join our Discord and we will attempt to answer any questions you have! https://discord.gg/2xZxuv2PxY
